ref=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;milestone=5.6.1&amp;group=status&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=status&amp;col=milestone&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=priority&amp;order=priority\">corrige 20 problemas</a> e também 7 erros no editor de blocos. Esses problemas afetam a versão 5.6, então é recomendado que você atualize para nova versão.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Você pode baixar o <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/wordpress-5.6.1.zip\">WordPress 5.6.1 diretamente</a> ou  acessar&nbsp;<strong>Painel → Atualizações</strong>&nbsp;e clicar em&nbsp;<strong>Atualizar agora</strong>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sites com suporte a atualizações automáticas em segundo plano já começaram o processo de atualização.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>O WordPress 5.6.1 é uma versão de manutenção de ciclo curto. O próximo grande lançamento será a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/5-7/\">versão 5.7</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Para ver a lista completa de alterações, você pode acessar a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://core.trac.wordpress.org/query?status=closed&amp;milestone=5.6.1&amp;group=status&amp;col=id&amp;col=summary&amp;col=status&amp;col=milestone&amp;col=owner&amp;col=type&amp;col=priority&amp;order=priority\">lista no Trac</a>, ler o post do&nbsp;<a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2021/01/28/wordpress-5-6-1-rc1/\">5.6.1 RC1</a> ou <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/support/wordpress-version/version-5-6-1/\">visitar a página da documentação da versão 5.6.1</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Agradecimentos</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>O lançamento 5.6.1 foi liderado por <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/audrasjb/\">@audrasjb</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/desrosj/\">@desrosj</a>, <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sergeybiryukov/\">@sergeybiryukov</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/whyisjake/\">@whyisjake</a>. Agradecimento para <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/metalandcoffee/\">@metalandcoffee</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/hellofromtonya/\">@hellofromtonya</a> pelo bug scrubs, além de <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/planningwrite/\">@planningwrite</a> e <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidbaumwald/\">@davidbaumwald</a> pela ajuda no post de lançamento.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Agradecemos a todas as pessoas que contribuíram para o WordPress 5.6.1:</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aaribaud/\">aaribaud</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aaroncampbell/\">Aaron D. Campbell</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/engahmeds3ed/\">Ahmed Saeed</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/azaozz/\">Andrew Ozz</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/antpb/\">Anthony Burchell</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/archon810/\">archon810</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/aristath/\">Ari Stathopoulos</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ayeshrajans/\">Ayesh Karunaratne</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/basscan/\">basscan</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/carloscastilloadhoc/\">carloscastilloadhoc</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/poena/\">Carolina Nymark</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/celendesign/\">celendesign</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cfinke/\">Christopher Finke</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/copons/\">Copons</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/danfarrow/\">Dan Farrow</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/talldanwp/\">Daniel Richards</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/davidbinda/\">david.binda</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/denisco/\">Denis Yanchevskiy</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dilipbheda/\">Dilip Bheda</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ocean90/\">Dominik Schilling</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/metalandcoffee/\">Ebonie Butler</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://profiles.wordp